Use MagicISO to decompress .uia file to .iso format.
Use IsoBuster to extract  files (or just burn .iso to a cd-rom). This gives 1 .exe file (the CS3 app) + 1 compressed archive, .zip or .rar (the keygen + small info file).
Run the .exe file. It will extract the Setup files into a temp folder. Remember where that folder is.
Open that folder and click Setup to begin installing the application itself. It will need 1.1GB for the installation.
